<br>
Usage:<br>
------<br>
Target player, activate Discipline.<br>
<br>
Description:<br>
-----------<br>
<br>
Halve the damage taken by targeted player, and instead deal the other half to the Paladin.  If activated on yourself this will have no effect.<br>
<br>
1 minute use; 72 minute reuse. <p><font color="0000aa">
