Good ideas coming out of here I think.. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udaanya.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daanya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 49<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/17/02 5:27:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15268.topic&index=28>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> How to fix pallies</span><hr size=1> Shields (for PAL / SK only):<br>
- Innate +100% dodge, +100% parry.<br>
- Innate &quot;Bash Riposte&quot; based off riposte skill.<br>
- Innate 10% damage avoidance in addition to damage absorbtion (ie if you get hit for 100, and already have 5% absorbtion from AA, you are hit for 85 rather than 95). This is in addition to the already slight damage absorbtion from the AC of the shield.<br>
<br>
Weapons<br>
- Make special weapons that are neither 1h or 2h but rather one-weapon-at-a-time, but you can still have a shield. These weapons would base themselves off the 2h damage table. An easy way would be make them 1h with -100% dual wield, and then open them for warriors, rogues, rangers, and monks as applicable.<br>
- Add a only weilding one weapon damage bonus.<br>
<br>
Misc<br>
- Add a level / 10 % bonus to attack rating for PAL / SK. We still can't hit as hard as war / rng / mnk / rog, but don't think it's fair we can't hit as often either because of the lower weapon skill. 6% bonus to ATK at level 60 is hardly imbalanced either ;p<br>
- (Controversial, but I think it could work) Make hybrid spells stack with parent spells of the same line. This wouldn't just be for paladins either. SK dots stacking w/ necro dots and ranger regen / thorns stacking with druid versions would REALLY help a group IMO.<br>
<br>
Should just about to it. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udaanya.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daanya</A> at: 4/17/02 5:32:01 pm<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showMessageRange?topicID=15268.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=15268.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=15268.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15268.topic&index=28><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=15268.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.threadControl?topicID=15268.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=15268.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=15268.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><